query:
SELECT 
  u.id,
  u.email,
  u.firstName,
  u.lastName,
  COUNT(DISTINCT qp.questionId) as answered
FROM users u
LEFT JOIN question_progress qp ON u.id = qp.userId
LEFT JOIN questions q ON qp.questionId = q.id AND q.courseId = 2
GROUP BY u.id
HAVING answered > 0
ORDER BY answered DESC;
